illa, España","global_code":"8C9P92R2+HW"},"rating":4.9,"reference":"ChIJMUirZEptEg0RFY0ufyUItyw","reviews":[{"author_name":"Lorival Gomes Martello","author_url":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/112080542964609223246/reviews","language":"es","original_language":"es","profile_photo_url":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ACB-R5SzRD-a_uRuLe3hIoPiaCZl4NT444JQnxlOuX9qHA=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4","rating":5,"relative_time_description":"Hace 2 meses","text":"English Version below:\n\nCasa de cambio pequeña, pero bien ubicada y muy útil. Te ofrecen buenos tipos de cambio que pueden mejorar según el importe, como es de esperar, claro. La asistente que me atendió, Belén, fue muy servicial aunque yo no fui muy amable, porque tenía prisa por ir a trabajar. Se lo recomiendo a todo aquel que necesite este servicio, seguro que volveré siempre que lo necesite.\n\nSmall currency exchange office, but well located and very useful. They offer you good exchange rates that can improve according to the amount, as is to be expected, of course. The attendant who helped me, Belén, was very helpful even though I wasn't very friendly, because I was in a hurry to go to work. I recommend it to everyone who needs this service, I will surely come back whenever I need it.","time":1678982018,"translated":false},{"author_name":"LEONOR HIDALGO YERGA","author_url":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/110727010829613209443/reviews","language":"es","original_language":"es","profile_photo_url":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ACB-R5RXpz1MGyQ2MtnGQYgOiECbDuzz_w6oDqcK4up_uA=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo","rating":5,"relative_time_description":"Hace 2 meses","text":"Son profesionales y confianza en el trato.\nMejor precio del mercado en Sevilla.\nSara, la dependienta q me atendió fue encantadora.\nSi lo necesito , volveré a contar con su servicio","time":1677322443,"translated":false},{"author_name":"Inma Bizcocho Bañez","author_url":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/109535211020603565848/reviews","language":"es","original_language":"es","profile_photo_url":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ACB-R5StQl1DidfDjInZC3fDdQiU49guJauzPtN_u0CZ3qY=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo","rating":5,"relative_time_description":"Hace 1 mes","text":"100% recomendable, muy amable Sara, que me atendió. Muy simpática y atenta durante el servicio prestado.","time":1680688745,"translated":false},{"author_name":"Agostina Verdini","author_url":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/113592692193936931795/reviews","language":"es","original_language":"es","profile_photo_url":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/AGNmyxYO0ScNMc_mXjXx6PqM_g8pdwZ1soN92gUtF0ol=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo","rating":5,"relative_time_description":"Hace una semana","text":"Muy buen servicio y trato. Ángela ha tenido muchísima paciencia y me ha atendido genial.gracias","time":1683636801,"translated":false},{"author_name":"Jose Manuel Carvajal Nuñez","author_url":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/118244590684249436379/reviews","language":"es","original_language":"es","profile_photo_url":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/AGNmyxbs80kCNRqIT4yf2_0gDYJqZWfi2ZNS-8gJxuw=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo","rating":5,"relative_time_description":"Hace 2 semanas","text":"Muy profesional.\nLa señorita Belen nos atendió con mucha simpatía y profesionalidad.\nMuy buen precio.","time":1683051940,"translated":false}],"types":["jewelry_store","finance","store","point_of_interest","establishment"],"url":"https://maps.google.com/?cid=3222053015547448597","user_ratings_total":577,"utc_offset":120,"vicinity":"Calle San Eloy, 43, Sevilla","website":"https://quickgold.es/compro-oro-sevilla/calle-san-eloy-43/?utm_source=gmb&utm_medium=boton&utm_content&utm_campaign=sitio-web-gmb","wheelchair_accessible_entrance":true},"status":"OK"}},"__N_SSG":true}